messages: 6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:24): The DNA test just proved positive
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:24): You are the father of my child
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:25): You better be here to help raise this bastard
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:26): *a wormhole opens up and a man steps out*
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:27): So that is how it happened?
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:27): ?Yes, I traveled back to impregnate you, please forgive me...It was the only way.
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:28): ?For you, Karen, must raise the one who will lead the rebellion against the machines!
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:29): ?Susan, take this voucher for 1/3 off on sex change operations
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:29): ?It is only valid until next wednesday, so you must hurry
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:30): ?And now, I must go...the time spa c e con ti n u u m i s    d  e    s ta  ba l. ..   .
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:32): what have you done with Karen?
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:32): No, Karen died in the fire that day, not me
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:32): I would never do anything to her! She was my idol!
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:33): and you pretended to be her? all this time?
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:33): I know! I loved her too! She was amazing! Nothing was impossible for her
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:35): well, I haven't been 100% honest either...
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:35): You see, I am already a man
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:35): Either? But I've been honest about everything
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:36): Wait.. I knew you looked familiar
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:36): So you are actual the father?
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:37): and you are now the mother of my evil baby!
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:38): It shall be born with a villain 'tache
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:38): That's why he's been doing all those bad things
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:38): and it's first words shall be "moo hoo ha ha"
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:38): And he did have a mustache...
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:39): Well, that night was over a year ago
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:43): My name? Nope. We're not French
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:43): oh, I thought he was a summon from Final Fantasy 8
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:45): We get some pretty awesome tractors around here.
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:47): You have an accent! A hot one!
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:47): haha, if you like fields and small towns...
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:48): like hugh laurie and colin firth
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:48): Still you have an accent that is more attractive compared to us Americans
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:49): it's mutual, yank accent is considered sexy over here
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:50): Really now? Guess it makes sense.  We want what we don't have
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:50): Plus, I think we can both agree that australian accents are the sexiest
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:51): so how long you lived in NYC?
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:52): wow, I can barely stay in London for more than a few days
6d3f3308d11c3960860f5b1dc8f0c7a6 (02:54): Reminds you that the world isn't about you, but that there are so many other people in this world
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:55): tell me about it, it's easy to fall into a routine and assume that everything around you is the end of it
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:55): the end of it being fields and tractors
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:55): so listen, it's been awesome fun chatting to you but I got to shut down in a bit
5e07d539c6e9d55074dcac24b55e6739 (02:56): just wanna say it's always nice to meet someone mad as me
